<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Tablespace on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/tablespace/</link><description>Recent content in Tablespace on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/tablespace/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[Solution] ORA-01652: Unable to Extend Temp Segment</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/oracle/ora-01652/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/oracle/ora-01652/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="ora-01652-unable-to-extend-temp-segment"&gt;ORA-01652: Unable to Extend Temp Segment&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ORA-01652 occurs when Oracle cannot allocate space for a temporary segment in the temporary tablespace. This typically happens during large sorting, hashing, or index creation operations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The temporary tablespace is too small for the operation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A query requires a large sort area that exceeds temp space&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The temporary tablespace datafile cannot auto-extend&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A runaway query is consuming all available temp space&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="check-temporary-tablespace-usage"&gt;Check Temporary Tablespace Usage&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SELECT&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; tablespace_name,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SUM&lt;/span&gt;(bytes_used) &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1024&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1024&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;AS&lt;/span&gt; used_mb,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SUM&lt;/span&gt;(bytes_free) &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1024&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1024&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;AS&lt;/span&gt; free_mb
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;FROM&lt;/span&gt; v$temp_space_header
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;GROUP&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;BY&lt;/span&gt; tablespace_name;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="add-datafile-to-temporary-tablespace"&gt;Add Datafile to Temporary Tablespace&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ALTER&lt;/span&gt; TABLESPACE temp &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ADD&lt;/span&gt; TEMPFILE &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;/u01/oradata/temp02.dbf&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SIZE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;G&lt;/span&gt; AUTOEXTEND &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ON&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;NEXT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;G&lt;/span&gt; MAXSIZE &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;30&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;G&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="resize-existing-tempfile"&gt;Resize Existing Tempfile&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ALTER&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;DATABASE&lt;/span&gt; TEMPFILE &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;/u01/oradata/temp01.dbf&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; RESIZE &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;20&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;G&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="kill-runaway-sessions"&gt;Kill Runaway Sessions&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SELECT&lt;/span&gt; sid, serial&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;#&lt;/span&gt;, sql_id, temp_space_allocated &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1024&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1024&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;AS&lt;/span&gt; mb
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;FROM&lt;/span&gt; v$rsql
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;WHERE&lt;/span&gt; temp_space_allocated &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;100&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1024&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1024&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ALTER&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SYSTEM&lt;/span&gt; KILL &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SESSION&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;sid,serial&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;IMMEDIATE&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="optimize-the-query"&gt;Optimize the Query&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Add indexes to reduce sort operations
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;CREATE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INDEX&lt;/span&gt; idx_large &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ON&lt;/span&gt; large_table(sort_column);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Use hints to avoid sorting
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SELECT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;/*+ NO_SORT */&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;FROM&lt;/span&gt; large_table &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ORDER&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;BY&lt;/span&gt; col;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Large sort operation
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SELECT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;FROM&lt;/span&gt; million_row_table &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ORDER&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;BY&lt;/span&gt; created_date;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- ORA-01652: unable to extend temp segment by 128 in tablespace TEMP
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Fix: ALTER TABLESPACE temp ADD TEMPFILE ...
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Index creation
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;CREATE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INDEX&lt;/span&gt; idx_big &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ON&lt;/span&gt; huge_table(col);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- ORA-01652: unable to extend temp segment by 256 in tablespace TEMP
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Fix: increase temp tablespace size
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/oracle/ora-04031/"&gt;ORA-04031&lt;/a&gt; — shared memory allocation failure&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/oracle/ora-12899/"&gt;ORA-012899&lt;/a&gt; — value too large for column&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>Oracle - ORA-01653: unable to extend table</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/oracle/oracle-tablespace-error-v2/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/oracle/oracle-tablespace-error-v2/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;ORA-01653: unable to extend table occurs when Oracle cannot allocate additional space for a table because the tablespace has no more free extents. This typically happens when the tablespace is full or autoextend is not enabled.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Tablespace is full and autoextend is disabled&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Datafile maxsize reached&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Large INSERT or bulk load consuming remaining space&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Tablespace not configured with autoextend&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Temporary tablespace full&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Check tablespace usage:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SELECT&lt;/span&gt; tablespace_name, round(sum_bytes&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1024&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1024&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1024&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt; used_gb,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; round(max_bytes&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1024&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1024&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1024&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt; max_gb,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; round((sum_bytes&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;max_bytes)&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;100&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt; pct_used
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;FROM&lt;/span&gt; (
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SELECT&lt;/span&gt; tablespace_name,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;sum&lt;/span&gt;(bytes) &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt; sum_bytes,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;sum&lt;/span&gt;(maxbytes) &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt; max_bytes
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;FROM&lt;/span&gt; dba_data_files
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;GROUP&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;BY&lt;/span&gt; tablespace_name
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="2"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Add datafile to tablespace:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ALTER&lt;/span&gt; TABLESPACE users
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ADD&lt;/span&gt; DATAFILE &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;/u01/oradata/mydb/users02.dbf&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SIZE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;G&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;AUTOEXTEND &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ON&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;NEXT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;G&lt;/span&gt; MAXSIZE &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;50&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;G&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="3"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enable autoextend on existing datafile:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ALTER&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;DATABASE&lt;/span&gt; DATAFILE &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;/u01/oradata/mydb/users01.dbf&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;AUTOEXTEND &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ON&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;NEXT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;G&lt;/span&gt; MAXSIZE &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;50&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;G&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="4"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Resize existing datafile:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ALTER&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;DATABASE&lt;/span&gt; DATAFILE &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;/u01/oradata/mydb/users01.dbf&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;RESIZE &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;20&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;G&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="5"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drop unused objects to free space:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SELECT&lt;/span&gt; segment_name, segment_type, bytes&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1024&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1024&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt; size_mb
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;FROM&lt;/span&gt; dba_segments
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;WHERE&lt;/span&gt; tablespace_name &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;USERS&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ORDER&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;BY&lt;/span&gt; bytes &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;DESC&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Error: ORA-01653: unable to extend table EMPLOYEES by 128 in tablespace USERS
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INSERT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INTO&lt;/span&gt; employees &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SELECT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;FROM&lt;/span&gt; large_source_table;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- ORA-01653: unable to extend table EMPLOYEES by 128 in tablespace USERS
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Fix: add datafile
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ALTER&lt;/span&gt; TABLESPACE users
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ADD&lt;/span&gt; DATAFILE &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;/u01/oradata/mydb/users03.dbf&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SIZE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;G&lt;/span&gt; AUTOEXTEND &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ON&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/oracle/oracle-sequence-error/"&gt;Sequence error&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/oracle/oracle-tablespace-error/"&gt;Tablespace error&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>Oracle Tablespace Error</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/oracle/oracle-tablespace-error/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/oracle/oracle-tablespace-error/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="oracle-tablespace-error"&gt;Oracle Tablespace Error&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An Oracle tablespace error occurs when the tablespace is full, has insufficient space, or encounters storage allocation issues. This prevents DDL and DML operations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Tablespace is full (datafile cannot extend)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Tablespace autoextend is disabled&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;User quota on tablespace exceeded&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Temporary tablespace is full&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="check-tablespace-usage"&gt;Check Tablespace Usage&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SELECT&lt;/span&gt; tablespace_name,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; ROUND(&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SUM&lt;/span&gt;(bytes)&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1024&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1024&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;AS&lt;/span&gt; used_mb,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; ROUND(&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SUM&lt;/span&gt;(maxbytes)&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1024&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1024&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;AS&lt;/span&gt; max_mb
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;FROM&lt;/span&gt; dba_data_files
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;GROUP&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;BY&lt;/span&gt; tablespace_name;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="add-datafile"&gt;Add Datafile&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ALTER&lt;/span&gt; TABLESPACE users &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ADD&lt;/span&gt; DATAFILE &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;/path/to/newfile.dbf&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SIZE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;G&lt;/span&gt; AUTOEXTEND &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ON&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="enable-autoextend"&gt;Enable Autoextend&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ALTER&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;DATABASE&lt;/span&gt; DATAFILE &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;/path/to/file.dbf&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; AUTOEXTEND &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ON&lt;/span&gt; MAXSIZE &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;G&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="check-user-quota"&gt;Check User Quota&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SELECT&lt;/span&gt; tablespace_name, bytes, max_bytes
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;FROM&lt;/span&gt; dba_ts_quotas
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;WHERE&lt;/span&gt; username &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;MYUSER&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="increase-user-quota"&gt;Increase User Quota&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ALTER&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;USER&lt;/span&gt; myuser QUOTA &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;G&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ON&lt;/span&gt; users;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="check-temporary-tablespace"&gt;Check Temporary Tablespace&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SELECT&lt;/span&gt; tablespace_name, &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SUM&lt;/span&gt;(bytes)&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1024&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1024&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;AS&lt;/span&gt; temp_mb
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;FROM&lt;/span&gt; dba_temp_files
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;GROUP&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;BY&lt;/span&gt; tablespace_name;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INSERT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INTO&lt;/span&gt; big_table &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;VALUES&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;data&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;ORA&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;01653&lt;/span&gt;: unable &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;to&lt;/span&gt; extend &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;table&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ADMIN&lt;/span&gt;.BIG_TABLE &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;by&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;128&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;in&lt;/span&gt; tablespace USERS
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Fix: add datafile
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ALTER&lt;/span&gt; TABLESPACE users &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ADD&lt;/span&gt; DATAFILE &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;/u01/oradata/users02.dbf&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SIZE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;G&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=""&gt;Permission Error&lt;/a&gt; — permission denied&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=""&gt;Sequence Error&lt;/a&gt; — sequence issues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>